Transfer Tape with Plasticizer Resistant Adhesive F9465PC General Information Note Vinyl formulations dier and plasticizer types and amounts can vary The most common types ofPlasticized Vinyl contain low molecular weight materials   plasticizers which tend to migrate out of the vinyl In the case of adhesive bonding, these plasticizers migrate into the adhesive which can cause softening of the   adhesive and loss of bond strength over time    The possible eect of plasticizer migration on an adhesive bond can be predicted by accelerated aging for 5 days at elevated temperature 150F 65C Note Due   to the variability of vinyl formulations, we strongly recommend that the user test each vinyl substrate to determine suitability of the tape for the particular application    Natural and synthetic rubber materials such as neoprene and EPDM are also formulated with llers and plasticizers Note 3M Adhesive Transfer Tape F9465PC   does not resist the eects of these particular llers and plasticizers and is not recommended for use in bonding these materials Technical Information Note The following technical information and data should be considered representative or typical only and supplier.title: 3M
supplier.content:
The benefits of being a 3M Preferred Converter:

  • Access to High-Performance Products – 3M is the leader in creating products, such as 3M™ VHB™ Foam Tape, that improve lives, enhance homes, and inspire the innovation of tomorrow.
  • Employee Training – The 3M Converter University provides us extensive knowledge on 3M products and technologies.
  • Networking – Using 3M’s extensive network allows us to work more efficiently in all areas of our business.
  • Extended Customer Benefits – We receive discounts and favorable lead times, which we extend to our customers.
  • Advisory Board Membership – SRP is on the 3M Advisory Board for Converter Markets.
  • 3M Innovation Center – We have access to the 3M Innovation Center in St. Paul, MN to give our customers a look at 3M’s new and existing technologies.
  • Support – As a Preferred Converter, SRP is supported by a team of 3M sales representatives.

From repositionable to permanent, 3M adhesive tape can be readily matched to the substrate and stress characteristics needed in the joint. Our custom fabricated 3M adhesives and tapes products can provide many solutions to countless applications using an array of different types of materials by converting them into custom gaskets and seals.
supplier.description: Over 50 years working with 3M gives us the opportunity to provide you VIP service from material sampling to prototyping—to full manufacturing, packaging, and delivery.
